<p>Media rules affect people with the Media rank.</p>

<h2>Streaming and recording</h2>

<p>Streaming and recording on the server is allowed and encouraged.</p>

<h2>Content restrictions</h2>

<p>Do not stream or upload content that shows exploits, cheats, or bug abuse.</p>

<h2>Privacy and respect</h2>

<p>Do not show or leak staff-only information, commands, or private areas.</p>

<h2>Respect and conduct</h2>

