<h2>General guidelines</h2>

<p>Follow all server rules and platform rules (Twitch, YouTube, TikTok, etc.).</p>

<h2>Additional rules</h2>

<p>Staff may ask you to stop recording or mute parts if sensitive information is involved.</p>

<h2>False accusations and impersonation</h2>

<p>Using media to falsely accuse players or staff is not allowed.</p>

<h2>Impersonation and branding</h2>

<p>The server name and branding may be used, but impersonation of staff or the server is forbidden.</p>

<h2>Base ratings</h2>

<p>If a player asks media to rate or review their base, the media creator is strictly forbidden from:</p>

<ul>
    <li>raiding or griefing the base</li>
    <li>leaking the base location or layout</li>
    <li>saving, sharing, or using the base information later</li>
    <li>using the rating for personal or group advantage</li>
</ul>

<h2>Consequences</h2>

<p>Any abuse of base ratings will result in serious punishment, including media restrictions or bans.</p>

